OLD CUTLER GLEN HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION, INC., Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
MICHAEL WEINER M.D. P.A. PROFIT SHARING PLAN, et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1033 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 30, 2017 LOGUE, LUCK and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Upon consideration, appellant's motion for rehearing of order dismissing appeal dated October 30, 2017 is hereby denied.
